<script>
    /**
     * Function that tracks a click on an outbound link in Analytics.
     * This function takes a valid URL string as an argument, and uses that URL string
     * as the event label. Setting the transport method to 'beacon' lets the hit be sent
     * using 'navigator.sendBeacon' in browser that support it.
     */
    var trackOutboundLink = function(url) {
        ga('send', 'event', 'outbound', 'click', url, {
            'transport': 'beacon',
            'hitCallback': function(){document.location = url;}
        });
    };
    var trackCampaignImpression = function(name, location) {
        ga('send', {
            hitType: 'event',
            eventCategory: "campaign-"+name,
            eventAction: 'impression',
            eventLabel: (window.location.href === undefined? "unknown" : window.location.href)
        });
    };
    var trackCampaignBotPageImpression = function(name) {
        ga('send', {
            hitType: 'event',
            eventCategory: "campaign-"+name,
            eventAction: 'botPageImpression',
            eventLabel: (window.location.href === undefined? "unknown" : window.location.href)
        });
    };
    var trackCampaignServerJoin = function(name) {

        ga('send', {
            hitType: 'event',
            eventCategory: "campaign-"+name,
            eventAction: 'serverJoin',
            eventLabel: (window.location.href === undefined? "unknown" : window.location.href)
        });
    };
    var trackCampaignWebClick = function(name, label) {
        if(label === undefined) {
            label = (window.location.href === undefined? "unknown" : window.location.href);
        }

        ga('send', {
            hitType: 'event',
            eventCategory: "campaign-"+name,
            eventAction: 'webClick',
            eventLabel: (window.location.href === undefined? "unknown" : window.location.href)
        });
    };
    var trackRegularServerJoin = function(name) {

        ga('send', {
            hitType: 'event',
            eventCategory: "organic-"+name,
            eventAction: 'serverJoin',
            eventLabel: (window.location.href === undefined? "unknown" : window.location.href)
        });
    };
    var trackRegularWebClick = function(name, label) {
        if(label === undefined) {
            label = (window.location.href === undefined? "unknown" : window.location.href);
        }


        ga('send', {
            hitType: 'event',
            eventCategory: "organic-"+name,
            eventAction: 'webClick',
            eventLabel: label
        });
    }
    var trackRegularBotPageImpression = function(name) {
        ga('send', {
            hitType: 'event',
            eventCategory: "organic-"+name,
            eventAction: 'botPageImpression',
            eventLabel: (window.location.href === undefined? "unknown" : window.location.href)
        });
    };
    var trackUpvote = function(id, label) {
        if(label === undefined) {
            label = (window.location.href === undefined? "unknown" : window.location.href);
        }

        ga('send', {
            hitType: 'event',
            eventCategory: "upvote",
            eventAction: id,
            eventLabel: label
        });
    }

    var myConfObj = {
        iframeMouseOver : false
    }
    window.addEventListener('blur',function(){
        if(myConfObj.iframeMouseOver){
            if(window.campaign === undefined) {
                trackRegularWebClick(window.botName, 'iframe');
            } else {
                trackCampaignWebClick(window.campaign, 'iframe');
            }
        }
    });

    if( document.getElementById('botiframe')) {
        document.getElementById('botiframe').addEventListener('mouseover', function () {
            myConfObj.iframeMouseOver = true;
        });
        document.getElementById('botiframe').addEventListener('mouseout', function () {
            myConfObj.iframeMouseOver = false;
        });
    }

    var setCampaignIframe = function(campaign) {
        window.campaign = campaign;
    }

    var setRegularIframe = function(botName) {
        window.botName = botName;
    }

    function fillsearch(filler, removeLastWord) {
      var search = document.querySelector('input[type="search"]');

        var temp = search.value.split(' ');

    function processInsides() {
      var words = searchbar.value.split(' ');
      var lastWord = words[words.length-1];
      if ((words[words.length-2] && words[words.length-2].startsWith('tag:')) || (words[words.length-1] && words[words.length-1].startsWith('tag:'))) {
        document.getElementById('searchoptionlist').style.display = 'none';
        document.getElementById('searchtaglist').style.display = 'block';
        document.getElementById('searchliblist').style.display = 'none';
        filterSuggestions('tag', lastWord, words[words.length-2] != 'tag:');
      } else if((words[words.length-2] && words[words.length-2].startsWith('library:')) || (words[words.length-1] && words[words.length-1].startsWith('library:'))) {
        document.getElementById('searchoptionlist').style.display = 'none';
        document.getElementById('searchtaglist').style.display = 'none';
        document.getElementById('searchliblist').style.display = 'block';
        filterSuggestions('library', lastWord, words[words.length-2] != 'library:');
      } else {
        document.getElementById('searchoptionlist').style.display = 'block';
        document.getElementById('searchtaglist').style.display = 'none';
        document.getElementById('searchliblist').style.display = 'none';
        filterSuggestions('tag', lastWord, words[words.length-2] != 'tag:');
        filterSuggestions('library', lastWord, words[words.length-2] != 'library:');
      }
      searchbar.value.includes('library:') ? library.style.display = 'none' : library.style.display = 'block';
    }
    
    function filterSuggestions(type, input, includeTagFill) {
      var validSet = type == 'tag' ? validTags : validLibs;
      if (input && input != 'tag:' && input != 'library:') {
        input = input.replace('tag:', '');
        input = input.replace('library:', '');
        var suggestions = validSet.filter(function(t){return t.toLowerCase().startsWith(input.toLowerCase())});
      } else {
        var suggestions = validSet;
      }
      suggestions = suggestions.map(function(s){if (!searchbar.value.includes('tag: ' + s) && !searchbar.value.includes('tag:' + s) && !searchbar.value.includes('library: ' + s) && !searchbar.value.includes('library:' + s)) return '<p onclick="fillsearch(\''+(includeTagFill ? type + ': ' : '')+s+'\', true)">'+s+'</p>'});
      suggestions.unshift('<p id="expandedsearchtitle">'+(type == 'tag' ? 'Tags' : 'Libraries')+'</p>');
      (type == 'tag' ? searchtaglist : searchliblist).innerHTML = suggestions.join('\n');
      if (includeTagFill && input && input != "tag:" && input != "library:" && suggestions.length != 1) {
        (type == 'tag' ? searchtaglist : searchliblist).style.display = 'block';
      } else if (includeTagFill && input && input != "tag:" && input != "library:" && suggestions.length == 1) {
        (type == 'tag' ? searchtaglist : searchliblist).style.display = 'none';
      }
    }

      }, 75);

    function request(opts, callback) {
        var xhr = new XMLHttpRequest()
        xhr.onreadystatechange = function () {
            if (xhr.readyState != 4) return
            if (xhr.status >= 200 && xhr.status < 400) {
                return callback(null, xhr.getResponseHeader("Content-Type") != null && xhr.getResponseHeader("Content-Type").indexOf("application/json") != -1 ? JSON.parse(xhr.responseText) : xhr.responseText, xhr)
            }
            var msg = xhr.responseText || "Error"
            callback(Error(msg), null, xhr)
        }
        xhr.open(opts.method || "GET", opts.url)
        for (var key in opts.headers) {
            xhr.setRequestHeader(key, opts.headers[key])
        }
        xhr.send(opts.data)
        return xhr
    }

        if (!document.getElementById('userloggedin')) return document.getElementById('upvotenologin').classList.add('is-active');
        var voted = el.classList.contains('voted');
        var monthly = el.getAttribute('data-tooltip') == "Votes this month";
        request({
            url: window.location.protocol + "//" + window.location.hostname + "/api/vote",
            method: "POST",
            data: JSON.stringify({
                bot: id,
                type: voted ? "none" : "upvote",
                ret: monthly ? 'monthly' : undefined
            }),
            headers: {
                "Content-Type": "application/json"
            }
        }, function (err, res) {
            if (err) return console.error(err);
            trackUpvote(id);
            voted ? el.classList.remove('voted') : el.classList.add('voted');
            el.children[1].innerHTML = res.points.toLocaleString('en-US');
        });
    }

messaging.getToken()
.then(function(token) {
  if (token) {
    return;
  } else {
    if (new Date() - Date.parse(localStorage.getItem('NotificationsLastAsked')) > 86400000 && localStorage.getItem('NotificationsAskedAmount') < 10) {
      ga('send', 'event', 'NotificationsRequested', 'frontpage');
      localStorage.setItem('NotificationsAskedAmount', parseInt(localStorage.getItem('NotificationsAskedAmount')) + 1);

      messaging.requestPermission()

        console.log('Notification permission granted.');
        return messaging.getToken();

        var xhr = new XMLHttpRequest();
        xhr.open("POST", '/blog/send_token', true);
        xhr.setRequestHeader("Content-type", "application/x-www-form-urlencoded");
        xhr.send("token="+encodeURIComponent(token));
        ga('send', 'event', 'NotificationsAccepted', 'frontpage');
      })
